		\end{array}\right|}{\left|\begin{array}{ccccc}
		1  & \langle N\rangle^a & 0 & 0 &\langle e\rangle^a \\
		\langle N\rangle^a &  \langle N^2\rangle^a & 0 & 0& \langle eN\rangle^a\\
